{% block title %}Interview for {{ speaker.name }}{% endblock %}

{% block content %}

    <p>Hello {{ speaker.name }}, </p>
    <p>You have been chosen to make a talk during the event {{ event.name }}, and we wanted to make an interview about you that will be publish on our website.</p>
    <p>If you accept, could you answer those questions below and send your response by email at community-event-manager@gmail.com?</p>

    {% for question in questionList %}
        <h3>{{ question }}</h3>
    {% endfor %}

    <p>Thank you for your time!</p>
    <p>Best Regards,</p>
    <p>The Community Event Manager Team.</p>
{% endblock %}
